----[ Purpose

	Display a text watermark at the bottom of all graphs

----[ Features

	PA 2.0 Compatible

----[ Installation

	Plugin is Plugin Architecture 2.0 only compatible
	To install, place it in your plugin directory in a folder called "watermark"
	Then login to Cacti, goto Plugin Management and click "Install" next to the plugin's name

	You can then edit the text under Settings >> "Visual" tab >> Watermark
    
